With both sides eager to start on a positive note, this match is set to be a fascinating contest where every inch of the pitch will be fiercely contested.
The most compelling bet for this match is to back under 2.5 goals. The data points towards a low-scoring affair, with both teams showcasing solid defensive capabilities in recent matches.
